      <h2 class="slide__heading reveal">Prompt Modifiers</h2>
      <p class="km-section-intro fade-in">Append these modifiers to any prompt to shift the aesthetic. Group by axis &mdash; lighting, materials, atmosphere &mdash; and combine as needed.</p>

      <div class="km-card-grid km-card-grid--3 stagger-children">
        <div class="km-rule">
          <div class="km-rule__title">Lighting</div>
          <div class="km-rule__text" style="margin-bottom:8px"><strong style="color:var(--fx-base-200)">Warmer:</strong> shift to 2700K tungsten, more walnut and leather, increase shadow depth, evening atmosphere.</div>
          <div class="km-rule__text"><strong style="color:var(--fx-base-200)">Colder / Clinical:</strong> shift to 4000K neutral white, more stainless steel and glass, reduce wood, increase contrast.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="km-rule">
          <div class="km-rule__title">Materials</div>
          <div class="km-rule__text" style="margin-bottom:8px"><strong style="color:var(--fx-base-200)">More LoveFrom:</strong> anodized aluminum, concealed fasteners, obsessive material junctions, no visible plastic.</div>
          <div class="km-rule__text" style="margin-bottom:8px"><strong style="color:var(--fx-base-200)">More Japanese:</strong> wabi-sabi aesthetic, shou sugi ban wood, indirect lighting, shadow-board precision.</div>
          <div class="km-rule__text"><strong style="color:var(--fx-base-200)">More Nordic:</strong> Sn&oslash;hetta architecture, raw timber and concrete, hygge warmth, natural light priority.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="km-rule">
          <div class="km-rule__title">Atmosphere</div>
          <div class="km-rule__text" style="margin-bottom:8px"><strong style="color:var(--fx-base-200)">More F1:</strong> McLaren MTC, carbon fiber, clinical precision, Pirelli hot-box aesthetic.</div>
          <div class="km-rule__text" style="margin-bottom:8px"><strong style="color:var(--fx-base-200)">More Southern:</strong> NC Piedmont, live oaks, red clay, tobacco barn materials, humid golden light.</div>
          <div class="km-rule__text" style="margin-bottom:8px"><strong style="color:var(--fx-base-200)">More Heritage:</strong> 1970s motorsport garage, analog instruments, hand-painted signage, Kodachrome grain.</div>
          <div class="km-rule__text"><strong style="color:var(--fx-base-200)">More Caf&eacute;:</strong> Rapha Clubhouse, communal tables, espresso culture, cycling warmth applied to automotive.</div>
